{"type":"message","id":"2f72518a","parentId":"9feac365","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:20:24.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Boss wants to chat on Telegram. I need to help them set up Telegram. According to the BOOTSTRAP.md instructions:\n\n\"## Connect (Optional)\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\"\n\nSo I need to guide Boss through setting up Telegram. This involves creating a bot via BotFather on Telegram. Let me explain the steps.","thinkingSignature":"91cb6b79022fba5a85f45b3953484dc9408fbba4a2d26d8f57cd57daee2cf62f"},{"type":"text","text":"Absolutely! Here's how to set me up on Telegram:\n\n1. **Open Telegram** and search for **@BotFather** (the official bot for creating bots)\n\n2. **Start a chat** with BotFather and send `/newbot`\n\n3. **Pick a name** for your bot (e.g., \"Ovo Assistant\")\n\n4. **Pick a username** — must end in `bot` (e.g., `@ovo_assistant_bot`)\n\n5. BotFather will give you a **token** — paste that here and I'll connect it\n\nOnce you've created the bot and have the token, send it my way and I'll hook it up! 🤖"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":256,"cacheRead":7817,"cacheWrite":6653,"totalTokens":14754,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771345216947}}
