{"type":"message","id":"4e490b96","parentId":"72f0eb6c","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:20:33.804Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"talk\" - they want to talk via Telegram. Let me re-read what I just said - I gave them instructions to create a bot. Maybe they want me to create a bot for them, or they're asking if we can just chat now.\n\nActually, I think I need to clarify - did they mean they want to set up Telegram chat with me? Or they want to just continue talking here? They said \"can we talk in telegram\" and I gave instructions. Then they said \"talk\" - maybe they want me to just continue the conversation here in webchat?\n\nI'll ask for clarification - do they want to set up Telegram now, or should we just keep chatting here?","thinkingSignature":"f68bba88e0f8daff2fb087b9aec8d1457fe8a21ff3a3fff9cdc4abdcb9e27d60"},{"type":"text","text":"You mean set up Telegram now, or just keep chatting here?\n\nIf you want Telegram, I need that bot token from BotFather. If you just want to talk — I'm right here! What's on your mind?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":188,"cacheRead":7817,"cacheWrite":6814,"totalTokens":14847,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771345225014}}
