{"type":"message","id":"55648a3f","parentId":"51277d5f","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:21:23.327Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Boss wants to set up Telegram. I need to guide them through creating a bot with BotFather and getting the token.","thinkingSignature":"c39c5945f4161c3d84dde91a6d2678ad3a50e17b5b9ea63b33913e153109e1e4"},{"type":"text","text":"Alright! Let's get Telegram set up:\n\n1. Open Telegram and search for **@BotFather**\n2. Start it and type `/newbot`\n3. Follow the prompts to name your bot\n4. When done, BotFather gives you a token like `123456:ABC-DEF1234ghIkl-zyx57W2v1u123ew11`\n\nPaste that token here and I'll connect it! 🔗"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":116,"cacheRead":7817,"cacheWrite":6888,"totalTokens":14849,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771345279346}}
