{"type":"message","id":"10b151c2","parentId":"a3ad8df7","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:28:23.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Boss is asking how to close the TUI (Terminal User Interface). They're asking if they should send \"exit\" to close it.\n\nIn OpenClaw, the TUI can typically be closed with:\n- `exit` or `quit` command\n- Or Ctrl+C\n\nLet me give them a straightforward answer.","thinkingSignature":"16c439e277ef249f60417ca2c07c349af1eb29d6b4b5d6361c9888fa690959fe"},{"type":"text","text":"对，发 `exit` 或者 `quit` 就能退出 TUI。\n\n或者直接 `Ctrl+C` 也行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":92,"cacheRead":7820,"cacheWrite":12163,"totalTokens":20103,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771345696741}}
