{"type":"message","id":"ba5a7234","parentId":"8898a049","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:31:49.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to send them WeChat messages for reminders. Let me check if there's a WeChat plugin available in the OpenClaw skills or plugins.\n\nI don't see WeChat in the skills list. Let me check if there's a plugin or if there's another way to do this.\n\nActually, I should search for any WeChat-related capabilities. Let me also check what's available in the OpenClaw docs or if there's a way to integrate WeChat.\n\nThe user wants proactive notifications to their WeChat. Since there's no built-in WeChat support, I could:\n1. Look for a WeChat plugin\n2. Suggest alternative approaches (like email to WeChat, or using a different notification method)\n\nLet me search for WeChat options.","thinkingSignature":"96c2cd2b60aba4336cf179d982c5422f295f36958532d4ead05326a5d513aa71"},{"type":"text","text":"目前 OpenClaw 没有内置微信支持。我帮你搜一下有没有现成的解决方案：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aznfr2boterr_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"OpenClaw WeChat plugin notification"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":200,"cacheRead":7820,"cacheWrite":12828,"totalTokens":20876,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771345899826}}
{"type":"message","id":"55884335","parentId":"ba5a7234","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:31:49.511Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_aznfr2boterr_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771345909508}}
{"type":"message","id":"5330096d","parentId":"55884335","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:31:55.243Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No web search available. Let me think about alternatives. \n\nWeChat doesn't have a simple bot API like Telegram. There are some approaches:\n\n1. **WeChat Work (WeCom)** - Enterprise WeChat has bot/webhook capabilities\n2. **微信机器人框架** - Some third-party libraries like itchat, Wechaty\n3. **邮件转发** - Set up email to WeChat notification (WeChat can bind to email for notifications)\n4. **Cross-platform alternatives** - Use Telegram as the notification hub, then forward to WeChat somehow\n\nThe simplest approach for now might be:\n- Use cron to set reminders that send to Telegram (which you already have)\n- Or explore WeChat Work if you have a business account\n\nLet me suggest practical options.","thinkingSignature":"0cd069d8f5f126395303585b8185b356c691f8e751bc8823da89908b61a43d65"},{"type":"text","text":"微信没有像 Telegram 那样开放的机器人 API。几个替代方案：\n\n1. **微信企业版 (WeCom)** — 有 webhook 可以发消息，需要企业账号\n2. **邮件提醒** — 微信可以绑定邮箱，开启邮件通知，然后我发邮件给你\n3. **Telegram 中转** — 你在微信里关注 Telegram 机器人，也能收到消息\n\n你现在最常用哪个？或者你用企业微信吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":7472,"output":249,"cacheRead":13483,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21204,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771345909511}}
