{"type":"message","id":"4632ef67","parentId":"dee36cbd","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:36:27.560Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is a big data developer looking for a job change and wants me to:\n1. Compile interview preparation materials\n2. Send the result to their email nohotnnn@gmail.com\n\nI need to:\n1. First search/web fetch to get current interview knowledge for big data development positions\n2. Compile the information\n3. Send it via email - but wait, I don't have an email tool directly. Let me check what I can use.\n\nLooking at the tools, I don't see a direct email sending function. But I can check if there's a skill for email or if there's another way.\n\nLet me first research the interview topics for big data development positions, then figure out how to send the email.\n\nCommon big data interview topics include:\n- Hadoop (HDFS, MapReduce, YARN)\n- Spark\n- Kafka\n- Flink\n- Hive\n- HBase\n- SQL\n- Data warehousing\n- Distributed systems concepts\n- Java/Scala/Python\n- ETL pipelines\n- Cloud platforms (AWS EMR, Azure, GCP)\n\nLet me search for more specific information.","thinkingSignature":"9e83c51f115f6deeae06566c83a84afcd0d13393c7480db5a8a08cc389ae6146"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！让我先整理一份大数据开发的面试复习资料。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_snvqmfas1p2h_1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.1point3acres.com/wiki/index.php/wiki/%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%95%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C","maxChars":15000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":347,"cacheRead":7820,"cacheWrite":13200,"totalTokens":21395,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771346175549}}
