{"type":"message","id":"b4cf3c11","parentId":"5bdd3fef","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:38:06.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No email tools available. I should inform the user about this and propose alternatives:\n\n1. I can compile the interview materials and save it to a file for them to download\n2. They could set up an SMTP server or use a service\n3. Or they could use another method\n\nLet me first compile the interview materials, save it, and then see how to get it to them. I can write it to a file in the workspace.\n\nActually wait - let me think about this more carefully. The user is in China and","thinkingSignature":""}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":8499,"output":0,"cacheRead":13483,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21982,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1771346208404,"errorMessage":"terminated"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3462e381","parentId":"b4cf3c11","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:38:35.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No email client is installed on the system. Let me think about alternatives:1. I could try to install something\n2. I could write the content to a file and let the user know where to find it\n3. Maybe there's a webhook or other notification method\n\nLet me check if there's any way to send messages. Actually, let me try to install a simple mail tool or see if there's any SMTP configuration available.\n\nActually, wait - the user said they need a VPN to connect to me. This suggests the server might be outside China. Let me just write the content to a file in the workspace and let the user know they can access it there. That's the simplest solution for now.\n\nLet me compile the big data interview materials and save them to a file.","thinkingSignature":"66f61fee037607e4b69f31adea59e3fd9a307900345490b0ce80f6f58d30c932"},{"type":"text","text":"邮件工具没装在服务器上。我先帮你把复习资料整理好保存到文件里，你可以直接看，或者告诉我怎么发邮件（比如 SMTP 配置）。\n\n---\n\n## 大数据开发面试复习资料\n\n### 📚 核心技术栈\n\n**Hadoop 生态**\n- HDFS架构、DataNode/NameNode原理、读写流程\n- MapReduce工作原理、Shuffle过程、 combiner & partitioner\n- YARN架构、ResourceManager/NodeManager\n\n**Spark**\n- RDD, DataFrame, Dataset 区别\n- 窄依赖 vs 宽依赖、DAG划分\n- 内存管理、 Tungsten 优化\n- 常见算子操作、行动算子 vs 转换算子\n- Spark SQL 执行流程、DataFrame 优化\n\n**Kafka**\n- 架构（Broker, Producer, Consumer, ZK）\n- 分区副本机制、ISR\n- 消息顺序性、Exactly Once\n- 消费者组、offset 管理\n\n**Flink**\n- 架构、JobManager/TaskManager\n- 窗口函数（滚动、滑动、会话）\n- Time (Event Time vs Processing Time) & Watermark\n- 状态管理 (Keyed State vs Operator State)\n- Checkpoint & Savepoint\n\n**Hive**\n- HQL执行流程、Metastore\n- 存储格式 (ORC, Parquet, TextFile)\n- 优化技巧（分区、桶、JOIN优化）\n\n**HBase**\n- 架构、RegionServer/Region\n- RowKey 设计原则\n- 读写流程、MemStore/StoreFile\n\n---\n\n### 💻 编程基础\n\n**Java**\n- 集合源码 (HashMap, ConcurrentHashMap, ArrayList)\n- JVM内存模型、GC算法、垃圾收集器\n- 多线程、并发包 (AQS, ThreadPoolExecutor)\n- 设计模式\n\n**SQL**\n- SQL执行顺序、JOIN优化\n- 窗口函数\n- 数据倾斜处理\n\n**Python/Scala** (可选)\n- PySpark API\n- Scala函数式编程\n\n---\n\n### 🏗️ 系统设计\n\n- 数据仓库分层（ODS → DWD → DWS → ADS）\n- 离线 vs 实时数仓\n- CDC (Change Data Capture)\n- 数据治理、元数据管理\n- 常见大数据项目架构设计\n\n---\n\n### ☁️ 云平台 (可选)\n\n- AWS EMR, Azure Databricks, GCP Dataproc\n- 阿里云 MaxCompute / DataWorks\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 常见面试题\n\n1. Spark Shuffle 原理及优化\n2. Kafka 消息不丢失如何保证\n3. 数据倾斜原因及解决方案\n4. Flink Checkpoint 原理\n5. HDFS 读写流程\n6. Spark 内存管理机制\n7. Kafka 分区再均衡\n8. 如何处理乱序消息\n\n---\n\n要我把这些保存到文件里吗？或者你能提供一个发邮件的方式？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":8499,"output":760,"cacheRead":13483,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22742,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771346289005}}
