{"type":"message","id":"4c7a23e9","parentId":"6029c310","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:46:40.426Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants:\n1. Configure email SMTP first\n2. Then search for high-quality study materials on the topics I listed (not just titles but actual content)\n\nLet me first check if there's an email plugin or skill available, and help configure SMTP. Then I'll need to search the web for actual study materials.\n\nFirst, let me check what's available for email:","thinkingSignature":"bfce5a2eaadda034f4bcba2dd2a58f0825195ac21ea6b5da2421f85ecb257f1f"},{"type":"text","text":"好，我先帮你配置 SMTP 邮件。你用什么邮箱？Gmail, QQ, 网易，还是企业邮箱？\n\n告诉我：\n1. 邮箱地址\n2. SMTP 服务器和端口（一般邮箱官网能找到）\n3. 密码或授权码\n\n配好了我就去帮你搜高质量的学习资料！📚"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":139,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":22145,"totalTokens":22312,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771346795110}}
