{"type":"message","id":"b5c7598e","parentId":"52414a66","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:47:28.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Boss wants to use Gmail. I need to give him the info he needs to set up an app password for Gmail, since Gmail requires OAuth or app-specific passwords for SMTP.\n\nGmail SMTP:\n- Server: smtp.gmail.com\n- Port: 587 (TLS) or 465 (SSL)\n- For SMTP, he needs to generate an \"App Password\" - he needs to enable 2FA first, then generate an app password.\n\nLet me give him clear instructions.","thinkingSignature":"f2177a3abf56df233f972fd027659d84176c0faba2f314e793434ff7d4ef3cfb"},{"type":"text","text":"Gmail SMTP 配置：\n\n- **SMTP 服务器:** `smtp.gmail.com`\n- **端口:** `587` (TLS) 或 `465` (SSL)\n- **用户名:** 你的完整邮箱地址\n- **密码:** 需要生成一个 **App Password**（不是登录密码！）\n\n---\n\n**生成 App Password 步骤：**\n1. 开启 Google 两步验证: https://myaccount.google.com/signinoptions/two-step-verification\n2. 前往 https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords\n3. 生成一个新密码，复制给我\n\n拿到 App Password 后告诉我，我帮你配好 SMTP！🔐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":233,"cacheRead":7820,"cacheWrite":14406,"totalTokens":22487,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771346840390}}
