{"type":"message","id":"d567a00d","parentId":"716630e1","timestamp":"2026-02-17T16:58:07.811Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The email has been sent. Let me inform Boss.","thinkingSignature":"b22fe54a557a54d8b11a9db8afd7ab6868350a295d266ecda1439df5ef5db200"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定！📧 \n\n邮件已发到 `nohotnnn@gmail.com`，包含：\n- Hadoop (HDFS/MapReduce/YARN)\n- Spark (RDD/DataFrame/内存管理/Shuffle)\n- Kafka (架构/ISR/Exactly Once)\n- Flink (窗口/时间语义/状态管理/Checkpoints)\n- Hive/HBase 优化\n- Java 基础（集合/JVM/多线程）\n- 系统设计\n- 面试常问题\n\n检查一下收件箱！📬"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":24566,"output":121,"cacheRead":13483,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38170,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771347483748}}
