{"type":"message","id":"85b6ced6","parentId":"1b9c2d09","timestamp":"2026-02-18T06:17:53.538Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah I see the problem! The website is returning HTML redirect pages instead of actual PDFs. The HEAD request worked (status 200) but the actual GET request returns an HTML page asking for JavaScript. \n\nI need to use a different approach - maybe using the direct PDF URLs that work. Let me check what URLs actually return PDFs.","thinkingSignature":"9c80849b0a3a2ca5c61ba6f9cb7fd5b977d68f3efe0db08c559ff1a5ba8d8896"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉！网站返回的是 HTML 页面而不是 PDF。让我重新找正确的下载链接：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dxz4c14ldvxc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport requests\n\n# Check what the actual download URL returns\nurls = [\n    (\"Direct chi\", \"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/chi/pdf/cap1.pdf\"),\n    (\"Direct eng\", \"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/eng/pdf/cap1.pdf\"),\n    (\"With A1\", \"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/chi/A1.pdf\"),\n    (\"Try export\", \"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/export?lang=chi&cap=1\"),\n]\n\nfor name, url in urls:\n    r = requests.get(url, timeout=15, allow_redirects=True)\n    print(f\"{name}: {r.status_code}, content-type: {r.headers.get('content-type')}, size: {len(r.content)}\")\n    # Check if it's actually a PDF\n    if b'%PDF' in r.content[:20]:\n        print(f\"  -> Real PDF!\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"  -> Not PDF, starts with: {r.content[:100]}\")\nEOF","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":62813,"output":343,"cacheRead":13483,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76639,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771395464669}}
