unt: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2N\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"nimble-pine","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Loading: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/index/chapternumber\nFound 20 law links\n  Interpretation and General Clauses Ordinance: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1\n  Administrative Appeals Rules: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1A\n  Fees for Official Signatures and Miscellaneous Services Notice (Repealed): https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1B\n  Specification of Public Offices Notice: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1C\n  Deputy Director of Immigration (Powers and Duties) Notice: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1D\n  Public Finance Ordinance: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2\n  Capital Works Reserve Fund: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2A\n  Capital Investment Fund: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2B\n  Loan Fund: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2C\n  Lotteries Fund: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2D\n  Civil Service Pension Reserve Fund: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2E\n  Electrical and Mechanical Services Department Workshop Services Suspense Account (Cancelled): https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2F\n  Financial Secretary Incorporated Suspense Account: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2G\n  Special Coin Suspense Account: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2H\n  Unallocated Stores Suspense Account: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2I\n  Correctional Services Industries Suspense Account: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2J\n  Electrical and Mechanical Services Department Suspense Account (Cancelled): https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2K\n  Disaster Relief Fund: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2L\n  Fees for Official Signatures and Miscellaneous Services Notice: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2M\n  Water Supplies Department Suspense Account: https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap2N\n","name":"python3 /root/.openclaw/workspace/scrape_hk_laws12.py"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771398082815}}
{"type":"message","id":"d55dbcef","parentId":"c75aa74c","timestamp":"2026-02-18T07:01:38.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the correct URL pattern:\n- `https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1` (not `/chi/cap1.html`)\n- The chapter numbers have suffixes like A, B, C etc for amendments\n\nNow let me write a scraper to get all the laws and try to download PDFs.","thinkingSignature":"8085874b7f84731714058427abe0e40e0d60d52c292b7e8320555d3c74b8adb4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zl8hp2ji06oy_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nHK Laws - Full scraper with correct URLs\n\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport time\nimport requests\nfrom selenium import webdriver\nfrom selenium.webdriver.chrome.options import Options\nfrom selenium.webdriver.common.by import By\n\nchrome_options = Options()\nchrome_options.add_argument(\"--headless\")\nchrome_options.add_argument(\"--no-sandbox\")\nchrome_options.add_argument(\"--disable-dev-shm-usage\")\nchrome_options.add_argument(\"--disable-gpu\")\nchrome_options.add_argument(\"--window-size=1920,1080\")\nchrome_options.add_argument(\"user-agent=Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36\")\n\ndriver = webdriver.Chrome(options=chrome_options)\n\nOUTPUT_DIR = \"/root/.openclaw/workspace/hk-laws-pdf\"\nos.makedirs(OUTPUT_DIR, exist_ok=True)\n\ndef get_all_laws():\n    \"\"\"Get all law URLs from index\"\"\"\n    url = \"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/index/chapternumber\"\n    driver.get(url)\n    time.sleep(5)\n    \n    links = driver.find_elements(By.TAG_NAME, \"a\")\n    laws = []\n    \n    for link in links:\n        try:\n            href = link.get_attribute(\"href\") or \"\"\n            text = link.text.strip()\n            if \"hk/cap\" in href and text and \"cap\" in href.lower():\n                laws.append((text, href))\n        except:\n            pass\n    \n    return laws\n\ndef try_download_pdf(law_url, law_name):\n    \"\"\"Try to download PDF from law page\"\"\"\n    # Navigate to law page\n    driver.get(law_url)\n    time.sleep(3)\n    \n    # Try to find PDF link or get current URL\n    current = driver.current_url\n    \n    # Check if there's PDF format available\n    # Try adding /pdf to URL\n    pdf_url = law_url + \".pdf\"\n    \n    # Use requests to check if PDF exists (faster)\n    try:\n        r = requests.head(pdf_url, timeout=10, allow_redirects=True)\n        if r.status_code == 200 and \"pdf\" in r.headers.get(\"content-type\", \"\"):\n            # Download it\n            r = requests.get(pdf_url, timeout=30)\n            filename = law_url.split(\"/cap\")[-1] + \".pdf\"\n            filepath = os.path.join(OUTPUT_DIR, filename)\n            with open(filepath, \"wb\") as f:\n                f.write(r.content)\n            print(f\"Saved: {filename} ({len(r.content)} bytes)\")\n            return True\n    except Exception as e:\n        pass\n    \n    return False\n\n# Get all laws\nprint(\"Getting law list...\")\nlaws = get_all_laws()\nprint(f\"Found {len(laws)} laws\")\n\n# Try to download first 10 as test\nprint(\"\\nTrying to download PDFs...\")\nfor i, (name, url) in enumerate(laws[:10]):\n    print(f\"{i+1}. {name[:50]}: {url}\")\n    try_download_pdf(url, name)\n\ndriver.quit()\nprint(\"\\nDone!\")\n","file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/scrape_hk_laws13.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":82457,"output":768,"cacheRead":13483,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96708,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771398082823}}
