{"type":"message","id":"d6fc09cc","parentId":"e1fc3dbb","timestamp":"2026-02-18T14:50:36.037Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The APK looks fine. The launchable-activity is correctly set to MainActivity. Let me provide the APK and ask the user to try installing it, and also try to run logcat while they try to open the app.Actually, let me also think about possible issues:1. Maybe there's an issue with the app being installed but not appearing in the launcher2. Maybe there's an issue with the app being disabled3. Maybe there's some security setting on Xiaomi phones that blocks apps\n\nLet me ask the user to check a few things.","thinkingSignature":"2207d808031898d8baac9b5012533a7237f7c4250dcfcc34f363856d97ca2f03"},{"type":"text","text":"这是最简版本，只显示 \"Hello World! App is running\"。\n\n安装后请检查：\n1. 手机应用列表里有没有 \"育儿打分\" 这个app\n2. 打开ADB运行：`adb logcat | grep PARENTING`\n\n或者在电脑上装个小米助手/adb工具，连接手机后查看日志。\n\n如果还是闪退，我真的不知道问题了 😅"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":123125,"output":187,"cacheRead":13483,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136795,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771426213860}}
