{"type":"message","id":"eb87789d","parentId":"5b07e819","timestamp":"2026-02-18T14:53:06.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself (OpenClaw). Let me give a brief introduction.","thinkingSignature":"01ecdf83551ee76e12b9fc8e96f13565ade3a87fd1199172656b6e895bbe057a"},{"type":"text","text":"我是 **OpenClaw**，一个开源的个人 AI 助手框架 🦞\n\n**我能做什么：**\n- 📱 帮你控制手机（截图、发通知、执行命令）\n- 💬 多渠道聊天（Telegram、Discord、WhatsApp 等）\n- 🌐 搜索网页、抓取数据\n- 📧 收发邮件\n- ⏰ 定时任务提醒\n- 🖥️ 远程执行命令\n- 📂 文件操作\n\n**怎么运行：**\n- 可以部署在服务器、电脑、手机\n- 通过 Telegram、网页等方式对话\n\n**我的特点：**\n- 本地优先，保护隐私\n- 可扩展的技能系统\n- 支持 pairing（配对设备）\n\n官方网站：https://docs.openclaw.ai\n\n---\n\n回到你的 App 问题 — 安装成功了但打开闪退的话，确实不好调试。可能是你手机系统或者某个兼容问题。要不换个模拟器试试？或者我帮你用纯 Web 版本实现这个功能？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":218,"cacheRead":7820,"cacheWrite":128608,"totalTokens":136674,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771426373237}}
