{"type":"message","id":"f3b3f525","parentId":"cdfff034","timestamp":"2026-02-18T14:54:33.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if my coding capabilities are self-developed or based on something else.\n\nI should clarify that I'm powered by AI models (like Claude/MiniMax) and I use various tools and skills to accomplish tasks. The coding ability comes from the underlying AI model, not something I developed myself.\n\nLet me explain this clearly.","thinkingSignature":"fcd66091312b673627a26c8f31cc18931b7ca842b7005ec11d96e1c5cb283b16"},{"type":"text","text":"不是我自研的。\n\n我是基于 **AI 大模型**（用的是 MiniMax M2.5）来帮你写代码的。\n\n简单说：\n- **我** = AI 大脑 + 各种工具（执行命令、读写文件、浏览器等）\n- **写代码** = 调用工具帮你创建/修改文件、运行命令\n\n所以刚才帮你写 Android App，其实是我调用了：\n- `write` 工具 → 写 Kotlin 代码\n- `exec` 工具 → 调用 Gradle 编译\n- 各种 Linux 命令 → 装 Java、Android SDK\n\n不是我\"自己\"会写代码，而是我\"会用工具\"帮你写。🤖"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":205,"cacheRead":7820,"cacheWrite":128818,"totalTokens":136871,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771426455506}}
{"type":"message","id":"d249fad0","parentId":"f3b3f525","timestamp":"2026-02-18T14:58:13.633Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"每天早上9点10分，自动发送过去24小时 A 股 机器人、人工智能再加一个最热门/热议板块的相关资讯，保证在开盘前掌握最全面的资讯，邮箱 nohotnnn@gmail.com，为了验证效果，现在先临时给我发一份看看效果"}],"timestamp":1771426693622}}
