{"type":"message","id":"9bf0f911","parentId":"74760c19","timestamp":"2026-02-18T16:05:43.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to add more news sources:\n- 同花顺 (iFinD)\n- 新浪财经 (Sina Finance)\n- 雪球 (Xueqiu)\n- 今日头条 (TouTiao)\n- 网易新闻 (NetEase News)\n- 百度新闻 (Baidu News)\n\nAnd filter for stock/finance related news from these general news sources.\n\nLet me try to fetch from these sources.","thinkingSignature":"7292d71aff35de5954b09343da2cbdb549a392a1075b2b94ee70a28f4bb44c66"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u7de38891anb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport requests\nimport json\nimport re\n\nheaders = {\n    'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36'\n}\n\nall_news = []\n\n# 1. 同花顺 (10jqka)\ntry:\n    r = requests.get(\"https://news.10jqka.com.cn/index.php?m=tag&a=getTagNews&tag=%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD\", \n                     headers=headers, timeout=10)\n    print(f\"同花顺: {r.status_code}\")\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        try:\n            data = r.json()\n            print(f\"  Data: {str(data)[:200]}\")\n        except:\n            print(f\"  Content: {r.text[:200]}\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"同花顺 error: {e}\")\n\n# 2. 雪球\ntry:\n    r = requests.get(\"https://xueqiu.com/v4/statuses/public_timeline.json?count=20&source=all\", \n                     headers=headers, timeout=10)\n    print(f\"雪球: {r.status_code}\")\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        try:\n            data = r.json()\n            print(f\"  Data: {str(data)[:200]}\")\n        except:\n            print(f\"  Content: {r.text[:200]}\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"雪球 error: {e}\")\n\n# 3. 新浪财经\ntry:\n    r = requests.get(\"https://finance.sina.com.cn/realstock/company/nc0103381/nc.shtml\", \n                     headers=headers, timeout=10)\n    print(f\"新浪财经: {r.status_code}\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"新浪财经 error: {e}\")\n\n# 4. 今日头条 (