{"type":"message","id":"6086057c","parentId":"84f55183","timestamp":"2026-02-18T16:54:18.863Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking who they should send a message to. They need to know the WhatsApp account that OpenClaw is using. Let me check what account is linked - from the creds.json I saw \"name\": \"nohothx\" - so the OpenClaw WhatsApp account is \"nohothx\".\n\nThe user needs to open their WhatsApp and search for this account to send a message.","thinkingSignature":"af87b687790b6f72829e586d7aa182a6afa774c6bd9b0e7d826c6465fff448fc"},{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 的 WhatsApp 用户名是：`nohothx`\n\n**操作步骤：**\n1. 打开你的 WhatsApp\n2. 点击右上角「新建对话」\n3. 搜索 `nohothx`\n4. 发一条消息（比如 \"你好\"）\n\n发完后告诉我，我帮你批准配对。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":155,"cacheRead":7823,"cacheWrite":65599,"totalTokens":73605,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771433651327}}
