{"type":"message","id":"4a257a82","parentId":"20473ce1","timestamp":"2026-02-18T17:08:06.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No pending requests. This is strange - the user sent a message but there's no pairing request. This might mean the dmPolicy is set to \"allow\" or the user was already approved. Let me check the session to see if there's a new message.Actually, maybe the user needs to approve the pairing from their side? Or maybe the message came through directly. Let me check the session history or just respond to confirm WhatsApp is working.\n\nActually, the message \"你好\" came through successfully - that's great! The WhatsApp is working now. The pairing mode might have automatically approved the user since they scanned the QR code.\n\nLet me just confirm everything is working now.","thinkingSignature":"283c6f8b05984247f714f112813e98647e3374ede4d397281f1911a2aa4e1d25"},{"type":"text","text":"收到你的消息了！🎉\n\nWhatsApp 连接成功！现在你可以通过 WhatsApp 和 Telegram 两个渠道联系我了。\n\n| 渠道 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| WhatsApp | ✅ 已连接 |\n| Telegram | ✅ 已连接 |"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":72801,"output":190,"cacheRead":13439,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771434479068}}
