{"type":"message","id":"5f6add25","parentId":"a8ccccf5","timestamp":"2026-02-18T17:09:22.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if messages from other people to their WhatsApp would come to me. Let me clarify:\n\n1. The user's WhatsApp (nohothx) is now linked to OpenClaw\n2. When someone sends a message to nohothx, it will come to me (the OpenClaw agent)\n3. But only the paired/allowed users can message - with dmPolicy: pairing, only approved contacts can chat\n\nI should clarify this for the user.","thinkingSignature":"62c88b75b37df2e1badb1cc02a2561848c4a62e4f21c2ae4a5ff1baf96c516a6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n对，也不对。\n\n**现在是这种情况：**\n- 你的 WhatsApp (`nohothx`) 已经绑定了我的\"大脑\"\n- **只有经过批准的人** 给我发消息，我才会回复\n\n**谁能给我发消息：**\n- ✅ 你自己（已绑定）\n- ❌ 其他人（未批准）会显示\"未连接\"或需要我批准\n\n**想测试一下？**\n让你朋友给你的 WhatsApp  发消息，你会看到：\n1. 消息会发到我的系统\n2. 我会提醒你有人发消息，需要你批准后才能回复\n\n或者你也可以再开一个小号测试。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":231,"cacheRead":7822,"cacheWrite":78439,"totalTokens":86520,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771434550516}}
